Load Test (k6) — 25 concurrent users × 3 minutes
10 Students — check classes, fees, attendance, notifications, dashboard
7 Teachers — list sessions, classes, dashboard, notifications
5 Parents — list children, child attendance, child payments, notifications
3 Admins — dashboard, students, classes, payments, enrollments
Thresholds: p95 response < 2s, error rate < 5%.

Runner Script
# Unit + security only (fast, no infra)
.\scripts\run-tests.ps1 -UnitOnly
# E2E only (needs frontend running)
.\scripts\run-tests.ps1 -E2EOnly
# All tests + load test (needs Docker + running app)
.\scripts\run-tests.ps1 -LoadTest
To run the load test, fill in tests/load/.env.example with real test account credentials, rename to .env.load, and run .\scripts\run-tests.ps1 -LoadTest.